    "description": "<strong>The Wishing Well</strong> features a standout combat system: determine your strategy by Math. This game allows you to <strong>calculate your stats</strong> with the key of &quot;The higher your points are, the more damage you deal&quot; <i>(In case that's threatening, it only involves basic Math!)</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Calculate your damage</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/b9352d6d3ef88c23a1e82dd7d0ce4fc0.poster.avif?t=1717524406\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/b9352d6d3ef88c23a1e82dd7d0ce4fc0.webm?t=1717524406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/b9352d6d3ef88c23a1e82dd7d0ce4fc0.mp4?t=1717524406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Perform a calculation to create your action and scale its effectiveness with the calculation result! Each operation links to a friend, which holds different abilities, and triggers them to attack when used in an equation. Your result will scale the strength of the friend(s) performing actions. Try out different combos in different scenarios!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover numerous actions</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/4829e522cf3dce3931f80a88cff97a22.poster.avif?t=1717524406\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/4829e522cf3dce3931f80a88cff97a22.webm?t=1717524406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/4829e522cf3dce3931f80a88cff97a22.mp4?t=1717524406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the world full of stickmen each with different combat styles and traits, both friends and foes! Embark on the journey and meet new enemies along with new challenges. Which one is the most fabulous to you?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unleash powerful abilities</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/02dee6742b207e29532cb8760b5399ae.poster.avif?t=1717524406\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/02dee6742b207e29532cb8760b5399ae.webm?t=1717524406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/02dee6742b207e29532cb8760b5399ae.mp4?t=1717524406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Upgrade and unlock various potentials including Ultimate moves, Consumables, and Perks to help you through this adventure. Prepare to embrace strength other than calculation! Who doesn't like that?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Retro style visual</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/d2ea1c1223f5396845bf1a9b3176761c.poster.avif?t=1717524406\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/d2ea1c1223f5396845bf1a9b3176761c.webm?t=1717524406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024170/extras/d2ea1c1223f5396845bf1a9b3176761c.mp4?t=1717524406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bring back the old-school cartoony art style! Experience the stylized stickman smoothly animated frame-by-frame in the colorful fantasy world. Let's enjoy every aspect of The Wishing Well!",
